{"tid":199854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得係咁打錯泰國做秦國班人好戇鳩?","createTime":"2017-04-13T13:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T13:40:46.000Z","uid":104148,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"121df1ed535334df02a645332d8120bad154a99e","tid":199854,"uid":104148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:23:57.000Z","msg":"成日喺連登睇啲旅遊嘢講泰國，總會有班人打咗泰國做秦國，仲要有班人柒下柒下若無其事咁講泰國點啊點啊。大佬話人哋講緊秦國啊，講緊歷史，你走去同人講泰國機場喺邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，笑死人咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會然們，當你見到有人打錯標題做秦國，一定要大大隻字寫住<br />\n<br />\n秦國定泰國啊，恥笑開始</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再鋪埋呢個po嘅link上去，得左</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc75fba68f4b2146dfe8993ce01f9844b6c61b67","tid":199854,"uid":104148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b25a9f5e35d7d0e1987ab168912067a7c7ec2d","tid":199854,"uid":62028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"打&ldquo;發覺&rdquo;做&ldquo;法國&rdquo; 戇鳩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373d04610649b6c53f326264da7356dde606eccf","tid":199854,"uid":104148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打&ldquo;發覺&rdquo;做&ldquo;法國&rdquo; 戇鳩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰啲懶型啫，打錯泰國真係柒到喊，係都要逼人恥笑開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b5d01cf239517ce0